Vulois

Vulois still was caring for Child when Windrazor and the Peace Angels
(maye we shoukd change the name, it's kinda crappy. You make it 
Alloran. Just nothing for fighting. We're a peace mission.)arrived 
again.

"Wha do you think? This is the new embassy. More safety, nore 
security, harder to find us. We're rebuilding all the equipment here. 
But before we do that there's an evil Child and I must face. It might 
be a horrible ending. We could be sucked into the black abyss. But I 
think we'll be okay."

Vulois put his hands on Child's body.

"Come on Child....feel the Matrix. Come back to us."
______________________________________________________________________
Brix/Fliq

Brix and Fliq tapped on the back of the shuttle.

"This back plate is holding most of it, but we still need more. Let's 
just scrounge up some rubble and than patch it together. I hipe the 
CF won't be mad at us."

Brix and Fliq go looking for suitable materials.
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream read the co-ordinates.

"Alright. Let's go!"

Starscream took off towards the Alliane base.
